# Rycode — Netlify redirects
# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# Proxy /grc/* through to the Rycode GRC Netlify site. The `200!`
# status is a rewrite (not a 3xx redirect) — the visitor's URL bar
# still shows rycode.dev/grc/... while the content is fetched
# from the origin.
#
# The GRC origin site is password-protected via Netlify Pro, so
# the proxy will pass the auth prompt through to visitors.
#
# The GRC project is named "rycodegrc" in Netlify, so its default
# subdomain is rycodegrc.netlify.app. If that changes, update below.
/grc/*    https://rycodegrc.netlify.app/:splat    200!
